  <a name="accents"></a>
  <h2>How do I write accents?</h2>
  <p>Writing special characters (á, é, ñ, etc.) is simple:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>On a mobile device: press the letter you want to place an accent over. In a few moments different options will appear. Drag your finger (i.e. without lifting it from the screen) and choose the character you need.</li>
    <li>On Macbooks: For Spanish accent marks, press option + e, then click the vowel. For the <i>eñe</i>, press option + n, then click n again.</li>
  </ul>

  <br>

  <a name="cookies"></a>
  <h2>I'm having login problems</h2>
  <p>If you see an error message when trying to log in, consider the following:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Did you create an account before attempting to log in for the first time?</li>
    <li>Are you writing the correct password? If you need a password change, choose that option in the login page.</li>
    <li>If you requested a password change but you haven't received any messages, check the junk folder in your email.</li>
    <li>If you disable cookies in your web browser, you will not be able to log in. Make sure cookies are enabled when you use Karooly.</li>
    <li>All Karooly passwords are encrypted upon creation: no one has access to a Karooly password other than the user who created it. That said, do make sure to write strong passwords, and to guard them.</li>
  </ol>

